üé® Design Tips

Color Palette: Purple (#6A1B9A), White (#FFFFFF), Light Gray (#F3F3F3), Green (#4CAF50)

Fonts: Bold headers (Montserrat / Poppins), Body (Roboto)

Use icons for SOS, lock, shield, alert, report, community

Keep each slide simple, minimal text, focus on visuals
